<p>Hi, I am Vimal and this is my submission to the IndexTank+Factual
competition titled <%= link_to "Srch!", "/maps" %>.  The idea is very
simple: enable local search and make it user friendly by creating a
maps based UI that lets the user quickly locate information about
businesses.</p>

