<h2>Feedback</h2>
<p>I liked the IndexTank service, but I felt at least one extra
feature would have been really good: Distance limits on Geospatial
Index.  That is, I wanted to be able to specify a scoring function as
follows:</p>

<code>
function:  miles(d[0], d[1], q[0], q[1]) < 10km
</code>

<p>It would have enabled me to restrict search results to within 10km
of the place searched, rather than the actual number of search
results.  It would help narrow search results much more effectively!
Maybe it is possible to use the <em>if</em> statement to
achieve the same, but I am not sure.</p>

